headline: Micron stock rises as Citi boosts price target ahead of earnings
summary: Investing.com -- Micron Technology (NASDAQ:MU) stock rose 3.6% in pre-market trading on Thursday after Citi analyst Christopher Danely raised his price target on the memory chip maker to $175 from $150 while maintaining a Buy rating.
